Google Lighthouse ko Google khud recommend karta hai, aur yeh tool 
web performance, SEO, aur accessibility ki testing ke liye kaafi popular hai.
Companies prefer karti hain kyunki yeh tool aapko detailed aur actionable feedback deta hai.

Google Lighthouse Features:*************
Performance: Page load time, interactivity, aur visual stability ko test karta hai.

Accessibility: Aapki website ko kaise accessible bana sakte hain, yeh check karta hai.

SEO: Aapki website ko search engines ke liye kitna optimize kiya gaya hai, yeh check karta hai.

Best Practices: Yeh aapko security aur other best practices ke liye suggestions deta hai.


Use **************(first method)
Google Chrome mein apni website open karein.

Right-click karke Inspect ko select karein.

Lighthouse tab ko select karein.

Generate report pe click karein, aur aapko detailed performance report mil jayega.

Use **************(second method)

(1)lighthouse http://localhost:3000 --view
(2)npm install -g lighthouse
(3)npm fund